caption.title: Analysis of binding properties of purified antibodies.
caption.p: The DEN-80E is coated on the plate for ELISA binding titration. The purified antibodies were diluted, and incubated with the coated antigen. The binding of the antibodies were detected by OD 450 with duplication. The curves were fitted by the one-site specific binding model.
